cs.CV, cs.GR, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MM 

The paper deals with computer vision and graphics problems, specifically new view synthesis from sets of real-world, natural imagery. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also involves deep learning, which suggests the category cs.LG (Machine Learning). The use of graphics and rendering techniques suggests the category cs.GR (Computer Graphics). The paper also involves the use of priors and automatic learning, which suggests the categories cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.MM (Multimedia).
